metadata.name: Stumbles - Revisited by William Takeover
metadata.description:
This is a variation of "One Of A Million Different Ways...", a tune I have been playing for 20+ years. Aspects of it sneak into a lot of the music I create, but I don't like putting it into a cage and calling it a "song". 

'Stumbles' was originally released on MintSongs with a different Winston pic and different audio, this is a reissued version under my own smart contract. The image and audio in this piece are subject to change whenever I may feel like it, but will likely be used for access to token-gated perks and events, etc. 

For more info visit www.WilliamTakeover.com

Recorded live on Clubhouse 09-23-22 

Duration - 1:14
